  <script language="javascript" type="text/javascript">
      var stri = window.parent.location.href;
      var strii = stri.indexOf('?');
      if (strii != -1) {
          var indexe = stri.substring(stri.indexOf('=') + 1);
          var pagename = indexe.substring(indexe.indexOf('/') + 1);
          window.location.href = '../index.html#PageName=' + pagename;
      }
     
  </script>
<body>
<div id="country3" class="tabcontent">
<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">

<h2>Nursing Station</h2><hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen will capture IPD admitted patient list of login ward. User can give treatment from this screen.
<br /><hr /><br />
<img src="images/IPD_patientsearch.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr />

<p>

<span class="title">Search: </span><br />
This search is optional if user want user can you use this search option.
Textbox is to write the value you are searching or looking for. Once it's done you can click on search button to get the result of your search. 
<br />
<span class="title">GRID (Display): </span> <br />
All admitted patient list will display for login ward order by patient admission date.
Based on search criteria data will display in the form of table. At a time only Ten (10) records will be displayed. To navigate or look for the next record pagination (the system of numbering pages) will be there. 
<br />
<span class="title">OK Button and Text Box: </span> 
<br />If user wants to switch directly to any particular page no, then he can simply enter the page no. in the given text box and click on Go Button.
<br />
    <span class="title">Option button selection:</span> 
    <br />User can select any patient and user can give treatment. Based on user selection user can click left hand side links.
       
</p>

</div>
